column5: http://www.theweathernetwork.com/news/articles/teenager-catches-record-breaking-16-pound-cod/64775/   Way to go kid! (Love reading stories like this. Between this and the story of the kid catching the Ontario record White Bass I feel like the kids are alright....... least some of em)

It's a beast.  Knowing that, I should've brought a scale with me last year, because I'm sure we got a couple that were solid 13-14 pound fish at least.  Anyways, good for the kid but I will absolutely crush that record in that short order haha
